{"id":4494,"date":"2022-03-21T14:28:19","date_gmt":"2022-03-21T06:28:19","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.acclime.com\/?page_id=4494"},"modified":"2023-07-14T09:18:57","modified_gmt":"2023-07-14T01:18:57","slug":"agility","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.acclime.com\/agility\/","title":{"rendered":"Agility"},"content":{"rendered":"<h5>Agility client portal<\/h5>\n<h1>Effortless corporate management with Agility<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h1>\n<div>\n<p>Agility is Acclime\u2019s complete cloud-based system to view, track and exchange documents for convenient collaboration, corporate administration and efficient management of every aspect of your corporate governance across Asia.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>\n    <a href=\"\/contact\/\">Talk to an Agility expert<\/a>\n<\/p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https:\/\/vimeo.com\/751102667\"><\/iframe><\/p>\n<div>\n<p class=\"uk-margin-remove-bottom\">Whether a startup, SME or an MNC, whether private or listed, today\u2019s business managers require their service provider to provide an elegant, tech-enabled solution to manage all of their outsourced corporate services across all the markets where they operate.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<h2>Experience complete control <br class=\"uk-visible@m\"> of your corporate governance<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h2>\n<div>\n<p>Login to our portal from anywhere to manage your corporate documents and administer the details related to your business and Acclime services.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/agility-dashboard.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>Insightful dashboard <br class=\"uk-visible@m\"> to keep you in control<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>The Agility platform features an insightful and customisable dashboard to keep you in control. At a glance, you get a <strong>complete overview of the most important data &amp; activities<\/strong> of all of your operations across Asia. Your Agility dashboard will keep you updated on all the outstanding issues requiring your attention and connect you to your Acclime account managers to complete the tasks.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/privacy-1.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>Swift &amp; secure access<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>Agility provides <strong>24\/7 access<\/strong> to your sensitive and important corporate data when you need it, <strong>from any device<\/strong>. It is fully built and maintained by Acclime and employs <strong>state-of-the-art\u00a0encryption<\/strong>, security and privacy standards (ISO 27001 certification is due later in 2022).<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div>\n<p>        <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/board-management.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3>Complete board management<span class=\"acc-orange\">.<\/span><\/h3>\n<div>\n<p>With a <strong><a href=\"\/agility\/boardmanagement\/\" style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">full suite of  board management<\/a><\/strong> tools available, you can manage your board meetings, store all your board documents, prepare and share agendas, compile board packs, digitise minutes and circulate resolutions for signature via <strong>AcclimeSign<sup>TM<\/sup><\/strong>. Agility will even set up and record your board meetings with our built-in video conferencing solution.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><a href=\"\/agility\/boardmanagement\/\">Learn more<\/a><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/agility.svg\" alt=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2>Explore how you can govern your business with Agility.<\/h2>\n<p>\n    <a href=\"\/contact\/\">Talk to an Agility expert<\/a>\n<\/p>\n<p><!--more--><br \/>\n<!-- {\"type\":\"layout\",\"children\":[{\"type\":\"section\",\"props\":{\"animation\":\"slide-bottom-small\",\"animation_delay\":\"150\",\"attributes\":\"\",\"css\":\".el-section {background: linear-gradient(to bottom, white,#f7f7f7);}\",\"image\":\"wp-content\\\/uploads\\\/acclime-dots-v3-rig